OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright start with plenty of
OL,6,Fsunshine. Cloud will build in the
OL,7,Feast, although warm, sunny spells will
OL,8,Fcontinue. Staying largely dry with
OL,9,Fjust a small chance of a few showers
OL,10,Fin the east during the afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA warm end to the day with
OL,13,Fsome late evening sunshine. Staying
OL,14,Fdry overnight with clear skies at
OL,15,Ffirst, but cloudier later. A cool
OL,16,Fnight for many.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
