OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FCloudy skies are likely at
OL,6,Ffirst during the morning, but quickly
OL,7,Fturning sunny in the east. Staying
OL,8,Fcloudy in parts of Devon and Cornwall
OL,9,Fwith a few showers.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,12,FStaying largely dry with sunny spells
OL,13,Fand variable amounts of cloud. A few
OL,14,Fspots of rain are possible at times
OL,15,Fwhere the cloud thickens. Very warm in
OL,16,Fthe sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
